         <abstract id="aspace_681c064822acd7354eff5a772e5eecfe">Collection of mounted black and white and color reproductions of Russian paintings. Content varies from original photographic prints to reproductions from magazines and other published sources. Some sections have accompanying clippings folders.</abstract>
